I"Á<h1 id="git-wiki-250---remote-theme">GIT WIKI 2.5.0 - REMOTE THEME</h1>

<p>This new version of git-wiki introduces a new installation method that allows to run git-wiki as a remote theme using this plugin: https://github.com/benbalter/jekyll-remote-theme</p>

<p>Such plugin is included in github pages by default so you can use it without any effort.</p>

